				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">You are correct; they were n00bs.
<br />

<br />
CoH clears aggro when the target is summoned sufficiently far enough away from the mob.  The actual distance has been discussed at length, including the assumption that summoning the target out of the aggro range of the mob is sufficient; to the assumption that it's a fixed distance regardless of the mob.
<br />

<br />
But 200 feet is a pretty safe distance.
<br />

<br />
And yeah, you were doing your job correctly.  CoH the warrior, then wait for the giants to wander off and tag one.  Works great.<br />_________________<br /><i>"Professor of archeology, expert on the occult, and how does one say it? Obtainer of rare antiquities."</i><hr><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=505 TARGET="_blank">
