				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">However, you need to make sure that no one has cast any type of debuff or other DOT on the mob.  Sometimes the puller will get a last second add and rather than continue to the camp, he/she will lead the mobs away to get coth'd and clear aggro.
<br />

<br />
Once you coth, you will clear aggro for the puller, but then the mob will return (many times with friends  <img src="images/smiles/icon_eek.gif" alt="icon_eek.gif" border="0" /> ) and look for the caster.  
<br />

<br />
Perhaps this explains some of the confusion and argument that you had with your group about coth ?
