				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">When in doubt I just use the Damage shield distance to measure CoH.\
<br />

<br />
If player is too far for DS its safe for CoH if in DS cast range I move away a bit, has worked for me everytime so far.
<br />

<br />
Nice thing about this is if target is out of DS range (so good for CoH range) you ll get the message right away and dont have to wait till spell is cast THEN get message.
<br />

<br />
Hope this helps <img src="images/smiles/icon_cool.gif" alt="icon_cool.gif" border="0" />
<br />

<br />
Downburst Stardestroyer
<br />
65 Arch Convoker 
<br />
<Infinit> E'ci</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
